In this folder we provide code for comparing ancestral reconstructions under BM and with the output of our MCMC. 

1- We simulate data using simulate_data.ipynb
2- We infer the posterior distribution using infer_posterior and run_mcmc.py
3- We infer the ancestral states and variances under a standard Brownian motion using fastAnc.R
4- We analyze results and compare using analyze_results.ipynb


